data.description:
MY SELLER WILL CONSIDER ALL OFFERS!  

This home is being sold AS-IS.

This desirable Aberdeen smart home comes with a high-tech security system and cameras.  The back yard has a screened in lanai and is in walking distance ST Johns County Schools.  

A few features of this stunning two story, 2,256 sq ft, 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home, include an open kitchen, living room and dining room concept, quartz countertops, and ss appliances.

The owner's suite has a tray ceiling, large walk-in closet, dual granite sinks, and a custom tile glass shower.  Upstairs you'll find a roomy loft, with 3 additional bedrooms and full bath.  

Ride a golf cart or walk to the pool, waterslide, soccer fields, restaurants, and other luxury amenities.

Schedule your appointment today!
